BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Venus trine Sun
DESCRIPTION:Transit Venus (Leo 20°41’) - trine - Natal Sun \nThis combination is ideal for going out and enjoying the company of other people. You will have great fun with friends, and you will be willing to help everyone. You will not have trouble expressing your love and you will want to impress the person you fancy. If you need help with something, now is the ideal time to ask for it. People will not be able to resist you.  \n \nTransit Venus in Natal 11th house: \nFriendship will bring you the most happiness during this transit. It is a favourable period for participation in group activities. You will feel great especially with people with whom you have common hobbies and interests. You will be welcoming and respectful towards others. You may even feel the desire to engage in charitable activities, become a volunteer or organize some beneficial group activity. If you are interested in someone during this transit, you will feel a strong friendship bond with each other, but the relationship may struggle on an intimate and deeply personal side.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260701T103100Z
DTEND:20260701T103100Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165735Z
UID:1_tr_ve_tr_su
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mercury square Uranus
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mercury (Cancer 25°58’) - square - Natal Uranus \nDuring this transit, you will not be able to slow down your thinking processes. You will tend to treat others with sarcasm and impatience. You will also be frustrated with your daily routine and monotonous activities. Therefore, you will tend not to complete tasks that were assigned to you. Your ideas will not meet with much understanding, which will contribute to your restlessness.  \n \nTransit Mercury in Natal 10th house: \nThis transit will force you to think about your future career path.  \nIt is very likely that you will want to talk to your supervisor about promotion, new responsibilities or plans for the future. If you do business, it is the ideal time to decide on strategies that will help you accomplish your professional goals.  \nYou will think about how your actions will affect the achievement of your goals in the long run. The details will not be very interesting for you because you will be focusing on broader context. It is also a great time to continue your professional training, you may for example decide to attend a course or a training programme. You will get along well with your colleagues during this transit, and you can help each other in professional development. This transit will be particularly beneficial for you if you work with technologies or engage in any form of communication. \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260702T110200Z
DTEND:20260702T110200Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165735Z
UID:2_tr_me_sq_ur
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Venus sextile Mars
DESCRIPTION:Transit Venus (Leo 24°26’) - sextile - Natal Mars \nYour relationships with others will be based on mutual exchange. This means that you will give and receive equally. You will feel comfortable with yourself, and this self-esteem will radiate outward. You will behave more spontaneously than usual. You will require more attention and try to reach your goals through making contacts with other people. You will do this assertively (not arrogantly or aggressively). There may be new friendships or romantic/sexual relationships based on sincerity. This transit is also great for expressing yourself with art.  \n \nTransit Venus in Natal 11th house: \nFriendship will bring you the most happiness during this transit. It is a favourable period for participation in group activities. You will feel great especially with people with whom you have common hobbies and interests. You will be welcoming and respectful towards others. You may even feel the desire to engage in charitable activities, become a volunteer or organize some beneficial group activity. If you are interested in someone during this transit, you will feel a strong friendship bond with each other, but the relationship may struggle on an intimate and deeply personal side.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260704T180800Z
DTEND:20260704T180800Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165735Z
UID:3_tr_ve_se_ma
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mars square Venus
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mars (Gemini 4°24’) - square - Natal Venus \nEither you or your partner will have increased sexual needs. The other person may not understand this and there may be small struggle for domination in the bedroom. In your career, be careful about any agreements that look too good to be true - you could be disappointed.  \n \nTransit Mars in Natal 8th house: \nThis transit will awaken the urge to change in you. If there is something in your life that you are not satisfied with in the long term, you will feel motivated to fundamentally change it. You will do this with the feeling of urgency. At work and in your personal life you will want everything right away and you will tend to be impatient. Be humble and make sure that your ego does not hinder your blooming relationships. If you make a living by trading, your business will flourish. \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260705T003600Z
DTEND:20260705T003600Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165735Z
UID:4_tr_ma_sq_ve
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mars trine Pluto
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mars (Gemini 5°03’) - trine - Natal Pluto \nThis transit will give you the opportunity to reach your goals because there will not be any obstacles that will complicate it. You will feel stronger than usual, both mentally and physically. It is therefore a good opportunity to test your physical condition by doing some demanding sports. Strength exercises especially will bring you the desired results. It’s also a good time to start a new diet or try an alternative way of eating.  \n \nTransit Mars in Natal 8th house: \nThis transit will awaken the urge to change in you. If there is something in your life that you are not satisfied with in the long term, you will feel motivated to fundamentally change it. You will do this with the feeling of urgency. At work and in your personal life you will want everything right away and you will tend to be impatient. Be humble and make sure that your ego does not hinder your blooming relationships. If you make a living by trading, your business will flourish. \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260705T222000Z
DTEND:20260705T222000Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165735Z
UID:5_tr_ma_tr_pl
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Venus sextile Uranus
DESCRIPTION:Transit Venus (Leo 25°58’) - sextile - Natal Uranus \nYou can expect pleasant surprises. You may meet someone you haven’t seen for a long time or you may experience something unexpected. You will yearn for new things and freedom. Restrictive relationships will now suffocate you. You won’t expect anyone to belong only to you, and you will expect the same freedom from others.  \n \nTransit Venus in Natal 11th house: \nFriendship will bring you the most happiness during this transit. It is a favourable period for participation in group activities. You will feel great especially with people with whom you have common hobbies and interests. You will be welcoming and respectful towards others. You may even feel the desire to engage in charitable activities, become a volunteer or organize some beneficial group activity. If you are interested in someone during this transit, you will feel a strong friendship bond with each other, but the relationship may struggle on an intimate and deeply personal side.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260706T025800Z
DTEND:20260706T025800Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165735Z
UID:6_tr_ve_se_ur
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Venus sextile Saturn
DESCRIPTION:Transit Venus (Leo 29°22’) - sextile - Natal Saturn \nYou will be realistic, and you will know what your responsibilities are. You will also be willing to sacrifice something and make a compromise to solve a work or a relationship problem. However, be careful not to be tempted by illusions and approach all matters objectively. This will have a positive impact on both your relationships and your work life. If you are now entering into a contract, it will be based on realistic grounds that will be beneficial to you. It is also an ideal time to ask for advice or to consult someone more experienced.  \n \nTransit Venus in Natal 11th house: \nFriendship will bring you the most happiness during this transit. It is a favourable period for participation in group activities. You will feel great especially with people with whom you have common hobbies and interests. You will be welcoming and respectful towards others. You may even feel the desire to engage in charitable activities, become a volunteer or organize some beneficial group activity. If you are interested in someone during this transit, you will feel a strong friendship bond with each other, but the relationship may struggle on an intimate and deeply personal side.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260709T035700Z
DTEND:20260709T035700Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165735Z
UID:7_tr_ve_se_sa
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mars square Jupiter
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mars (Gemini 7°26’) - square - Natal Jupiter \nBe careful of the tendencies to brag and arrogance that are supported by this transit. It provides you with great energy that you can use to promote your person constructively if you focus it in the right direction. However, if you follow plans that are too grand  and miss important details, your effort will be wasted.  \n \nTransit Mars in Natal 8th house: \nThis transit will awaken the urge to change in you. If there is something in your life that you are not satisfied with in the long term, you will feel motivated to fundamentally change it. You will do this with the feeling of urgency. At work and in your personal life you will want everything right away and you will tend to be impatient. Be humble and make sure that your ego does not hinder your blooming relationships. If you make a living by trading, your business will flourish. \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260709T075300Z
DTEND:20260709T075300Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165735Z
UID:8_tr_ma_sq_ju
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mars opposition Neptune
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mars (Gemini 9°22’) - opposition - Natal Neptune \nThis transit will make you question the direction your life is taking. You will not get on well with people and it is possible that you may get under the influence of people who will have a negative impact on you. It will be better if you spend time alone and relax. You will be tired and prone to disease. Your mind will be blurred, and you will not be able to think effectively.  \n \nTransit Mars in Natal 9th house: \nDiscovering new things, new experiences and adventures - that is exactly what you will crave. This transit provides an ideal opportunity to broaden your horizons and explore foreign countries, whether it means traveling, reading travelogues, trying new exotic food or going to a cultural festival. Your daily life may seem boring to you now and you will feel the need to change it. Throw yourself spontaneously into new activities, learn something new, and have fun! \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260712T020800Z
DTEND:20260712T020800Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165735Z
UID:9_tr_ma_op_ne
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Sun square Sun
DESCRIPTION:Transit Sun (Cancer 20°41’) - square - Natal Sun \nYou may have to deal with problems related to your plans and goals. The sun will uncover any mistakes that you made, and you will have the chance to reconsider your decisions and make changes. Beware of relationships with your superiors and of your big ego.  \n \nTransit Sun in Natal 10th house: \nThis transit shifts your focus to your career and goals! \nYou will behave more responsibly and start thinking about what you want to achieve, especially in your professional life. It is likely that you will ask for a raise at work, seek better career opportunities, or start thinking about starting your own business. During this transit your career comes first, and you will want to do well at work. You may be more in touch with your boss or discover a new mentor. You will also have more interactions with older people. You may even get involved with the government.  \nThis practical approach to life can help you advance your career but be careful and wise because this transit could punish you!  Be careful about your reputation and avoid all activities that could damage it.  \n \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260713T010600Z
DTEND:20260713T010600Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165735Z
UID:10_tr_su_sq_su
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Mercury square Sun
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mercury (Cancer 20°41’) - square - Natal Sun \nYou may be criticized, or you may receive bad news. Communication with others can be slow or lead to feelings of frustration. Try not to take things too personally and negatively. You should find time to relax.  \n \nTransit Mercury in Natal 10th house: \nThis transit will force you to think about your future career path.  \nIt is very likely that you will want to talk to your supervisor about promotion, new responsibilities or plans for the future. If you do business, it is the ideal time to decide on strategies that will help you accomplish your professional goals.  \nYou will think about how your actions will affect the achievement of your goals in the long run. The details will not be very interesting for you because you will be focusing on broader context. It is also a great time to continue your professional training, you may for example decide to attend a course or a training programme. You will get along well with your colleagues during this transit, and you can help each other in professional development. This transit will be particularly beneficial for you if you work with technologies or engage in any form of communication. \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260713T015300Z
DTEND:20260713T015300Z
