SUMMARY:Tr. Mars opposition Moon
DESCRIPTION:Transit Mars (Gemini 10°13’) - opposition - Natal Moon \nThere is chaos and disorganization in your home. Exceptionally, violence may also occur. If you have children, they are likely to try to see what they can get away with. Problems may also be expected in relationships with women. Pay special attention to your dreams.  \n \nTransit Mars in Natal 9th house: \nDiscovering new things, new experiences and adventures - that is exactly what you will crave. This transit provides an ideal opportunity to broaden your horizons and explore foreign countries, whether it means traveling, reading travelogues, trying new exotic food or going to a cultural festival. Your daily life may seem boring to you now and you will feel the need to change it. Throw yourself spontaneously into new activities, learn something new, and have fun! \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
