BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Uranus square Venus
DESCRIPTION:Transit Uranus (Gemini 4°24’) - square - Natal Venus \nYou may lose old friends or find yourself surrounded by strangers during this transit. There may be feelings of estrangement and inability to fit in. If you get together with someone at this time, it is likely that this relationship will be very volatile, and you will often break up and reunite. You may also get involved in a long-distance relationship. Stability in relationships will be something you will now lack.  \n \nTransit Uranus in Natal 8th house: \nDuring this transit Uranus brings unexpected developments in the area of finance. However, this does not involve the money you earn; it involves money you share with your partner (romantic or business), loans, alimony, taxes etc. People with whom you have a close relationship and whom you depend on financially may experience a period of financial instability. You may also start experimenting with your sexuality and change your opinion about intimate relationships.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
DTSTART:20260716T035800Z
DTEND:20260716T035800Z
DTSTAMP:20260403T165735Z
UID:14_tr_ur_sq_ve
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Venus opposition Jupiter
DESCRIPTION:Transit Venus (Virgo 7°26’) - opposition - Natal Jupiter \nYou’ll yearn for pleasure, nothing else will make you happy. You will be impractical, try to avoid possible problems and to please everyone. You should therefore try to maintain discipline and responsibility during this transit. You should also remember to do everything in moderation and not to take everything you have for granted. Beware of spending big sums of money on something just to impress the person you fancy. \n \nTransit Venus in Natal 11th house: \nFriendship will bring you the most happiness during this transit. It is a favourable period for participation in group activities. You will feel great especially with people with whom you have common hobbies and interests. You will be welcoming and respectful towards others. You may even feel the desire to engage in charitable activities, become a volunteer or organize some beneficial group activity. If you are interested in someone during this transit, you will feel a strong friendship bond with each other, but the relationship may struggle on an intimate and deeply personal side.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
