BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tr. Jupiter sextile Pluto
DESCRIPTION:Transit Jupiter (Leo 5°03’) - sextile - Natal Pluto \nThis transit is great for transformation. You may become interested in serious topics and you may want to start new things. You will do well in the area of finance, taxes and loans.  \n \nTransit Jupiter in Natal 10th house: \nThis transit is good for your career. It can bring promotion, increased productivity, better qualifications and success in your business. Sometimes it can also mean marriage because it is associated with a general improvement of your status. You will also have more freedom when you do your work. To maximize your success, you should approach things and people with sincerity and integrity. This will allow people in senior positions and in authority to be more inclined to positively respond to your requests. If Jupiter forms negative aspects, beware of abuse of power and prestige, selfishness and arrogance.  \n \nPersonal Transit Calendar:  \nhttps://horoscopes.astro-seek.com/personal-transit-calendar-monthly-astrology-transits
